com.parse.http

Interface ParseNetworkInterceptor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ParseLogInterceptor, ParseStethoInterceptor

    public interface ParseNetworkInterceptor
    ParseNetworkInterceptor is used to observe requests going out and the corresponding responses coming back in.
